            "id": 6412150,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 道瓊指數大漲2.56%，報47778.6點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間09日12:28，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>上漲1194.14點（或2.56%），暫報47778.60點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+0.52%</li><li>近 1 月：-1.93%</li><li>近 3 月：-4.92%</li><li>近 6 月：-0.04%</li><li>今年以來：-3.08%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>成分股以宣偉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SHW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SHW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SHW-US</a>)領漲。宣偉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SHW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SHW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SHW-US</a>)上漲6.92%；卡特彼勒(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CAT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CAT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CAT-US</a>)上漲5.84%；家得寶(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:HD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/HD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">HD-US</a>)上漲5.23%；高盛集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GS-US</a>)上漲4.33%；亞馬遜(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMZN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMZN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMZN-US</a>)上漲4.08%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，雪佛龍(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CVX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CVX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CVX-US</a>)下跌5.84%；威瑞森電信(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:VZ:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/VZ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">VZ-US</a>)下跌3.04%；國際商業機器(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:IBM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/IBM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">IBM-US</a>)下跌1.27%；聯合健康保險(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UNH:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UNH\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UNH-US</a>)下跌0.56%；賽富時(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRM-US</a>)下跌0.17%。</p></section></main>",
